project_descr: The project seeks to support the government in the development of holistic approaches that could help maximizing mine action results on human development.

outputs.output_descr: The project supports clearing of mines/ERW in poorest areas and establish mine action performance monitoring system that measures human development outcomes and progress towards achieving the status of free from the impact of mines/ERW for Cambodia.
donor_name: SWISS AGENCY FOR DEVELOPMENT AND COOPERATION - SDC
The Department of Foreign Affairs, Trade and development - Canada

project_title: clearing for results iii- mine action for human dev't
